Package: wickrashazam
Type: Package
Title: Data-Driven History-Fingerprint Match Core
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-shazam over its C ABI hub: build a Shazam from
    a spec JSON, index an asset's history and match the current fingerprint
    against it - the same protocol as the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-shazam
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-shazam/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-shazam C ABI shared library (WKSHZM_LIB) and its
    header (WKSHZM_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
